posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'A fabulous bedroom apartment home at an affordable price at Dove Tree Apartments!', 'You will be amazed at the price of our spacious one, two and three bedroom apartment homes.', 'We are conveniently located minutes from restaurants, various retailers and walking / biking trails.', 'Enjoy Lions Park right outside your door!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Adjoining Dining Room', 'And Living Room Area', '- Centrally Located Laundry Facilities', '- Unique Floor Plans', '- In-Home Air Conditioning Unit', '- Handicapped Accessible Homes (select homes)', '- Entry Way Coat Closet', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Dove Tree participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-4:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Dove Tree', '1105 Lions Park Drive', 'Elk River, MN, 55330', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '4oX9n5EJuux']
